{"tid":498667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"詩人余光中病逝高醫 享壽90","createTime":"2017-12-14T04:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T11:47:02.000Z","uid":35468,"like":96,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"67d4dbb40ea6b1997e3233e5afaa2acee3330c90","tid":498667,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:40:00.000Z","msg":"詩人余光中今天病逝高醫，享壽九十。<br />\n<br />\n余光中與范我存去年在鑽石婚的前夕，先是范我存腸道不明原因大出血，進了加護病房；隔天余光中在大樓門口附近跌了一跤，顱內出血，也進了加護病房。後來雙雙好轉，便以捐助弱勢團體的方式度過結婚60年。這一年來，詩人精神仍好，但身軀愈形瘦弱，進食也少。<br />\n<br />\n日前余光中疑似小中風又入院，肺部有些感染，後轉進加護病房，家人也從國外趕回，隨侍在側。余此次入院，家人非常低調，也擔心感染加劇，謝絕探訪。<br />\n<br />\n當天余光中談興極佳，大家怕他太累，想搬張椅子，詩人搖手不用，站著說完全場，直到夫人范我存在台下打手勢，才結尾開心切蛋糕。他看到許多老朋友非常開心，並以古人歐陽修的絕句「再至汝陰」抒發心情，「 黃栗留鳴桑椹美，紫櫻桃熟麥風涼。 朱輪昔愧無遺愛，白首重來似故鄉。」<br />\n<br />\n余光中過世，親友都很哀慟。<br />\n<br />\nRIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6fa3c800839440d4800e9341d3ddd478122eae","tid":498667,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:40:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7314/2874509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7314%2F2874509&d=oX%2FzVSq82eT82GbXMN2w9MmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=25b6251b\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7314/2874509</a>"},{"pid":"de30d70dc31efacf1fb969951dd7d40fa0f36f96","tid":498667,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"1aa5f75eb4aa7bb884340c149161eedbac325f0e","tid":498667,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2532d48de478b01b4c4227bb7a2d42930ad8c25e","tid":498667,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"38dbd14d68fb4358f38620b881f0ab34228e5ad5","tid":498667,"uid":101010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"R.I.P"},{"pid":"2ee48608bdc0e591607885f9833d21693a6f2862","tid":498667,"uid":20170,"like":5,"dislike":53,"score":-48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"Rip條撚？<br />\n上面啲人唔知「狼來了」係咩？"},{"pid":"3b7b2e3abc75eecc67514495fd9a762cfb2259c8","tid":498667,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"黑人問號.jpg"},{"pid":"bcb66a2b581d303629c133f81445dfda4ac2be4b","tid":498667,"uid":8729,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:46:21.000Z","msg":"佢係我老師個老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  rip"},{"pid":"be2c3e5f8a9c19c374a9a1302a212c1a6f93bd40","tid":498667,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec061cb535bcd128b2185987d32c458e5408b02","tid":498667,"uid":90863,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"國民黨文妓一條<br />\n<br />\n馬英九總統被國際知名的《經濟學人》雜誌評為bumbler，全臺輿論沸騰。余光中說，其實bumbler就是「拙」的意思，表示踏實、負責任、不輕舉妄動，如同大智若愚、愚公移山、大巧若拙，是媒體翻譯有問題。許多評論者並不認同餘光中這種觀點，如金恆煒即指出：余光中把「笨蛋」換裝成「大巧」，就像把大糞變成黃金，污辱了所有人智商，也把自己的專業踩在腳底。[16]沈政男指出：余光中英文不錯，但有翻譯莎士比亞全集的梁實秋好嗎？梁實秋編的《遠東英漢字典》裡說，bumble指的是「失敗、搞糟、喃喃不清的說」，哪裡有「大巧若拙」的意思？[17]"},{"pid":"79a4468dca129c93677c1e45d786752c8b664da7","tid":498667,"uid":70205,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 光中"},{"pid":"d1acba3aab140fb8eef443c29780a25e53a9ec1a","tid":498667,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 光中</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢罵鄉土罵得好, 成班師兄正on9"},{"pid":"b80e92a103ab0249e17fd453e0dd64943db03dc5","tid":498667,"uid":41655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT